{
  "texts": [
    "Tumor grades were also documented.",
    "Tumors were classified as low grade (61 cases) or high grade (68 cases) in the cohort.",
    "Tumor grades were determined as Cis (2 cases), pTa (67 cases), pT1 (49 cases), or pT2 (12 cases).",
    "Detailed information on patients and control cohorts was added as Supplementary Tables S1 and S2, respectively.",
    "Whole blood samples were collected from BCa patients and control individuals in EDTA tubes before the surgical procedures, and samples were frozen and kept more than 2 h in -80 °C freezers."
  ]
}